Resources

1. Hard resources [cash, equipment, information and data]
2. People
3. Time [Leadership time]
	-> to go out and manage, focus on execution and making sure things are getting done
	-> meeting your peoples needs
		* moral
		* culture
		* people development [skills, training, feedback]

* The tasks you're required to execute will drive the quantity of resources you need
	-> what you need to achieve
	-> whay you have today
	-> where you can balance for shortages

